# ---- Supabase Database (PostgreSQL) ----
# Get these from: https://supabase.com/dashboard → Your Project → Settings → Database
# Project Ref: bzvvxdmbswtdvdrzjyay
#
# DATABASE_URL = Connection Pooler (port 6543) - for app runtime
# DIRECT_URL   = Direct Connection (port 5432) - for Prisma migrations
#
# Replace [YOUR_DB_PASSWORD] with your database password
# Replace [REGION] with your Supabase project region (e.g., us-east-1, eu-west-1)

